aWFRuleDesc.RuleDescription:
When making a claim for damage that is covered by the policy to your own vehicle, a deductibel penalty applies based on the age of the involved driver
Penalty applies as follows: . Drivers aged 26 and over - $0 per claim . Drivers aged 22 to 25 inclusive - $250 per claim . Drivers under the age of 22 - $400 per claim . For drivers with less than 12 months experience , there is an additional $200 deductible per claim.
